entry.title: Ukraine's Leader Zelensky Is 'Target Number One' for Putin
entry.content: Russia’s invasion of Ukraine aims to overthrow the leadership in Kyiv, but President Volodymyr Zelensky remains defiant.

entry.title: Russian Forces Close In on Ukraine's Capital as Kremlin Agrees to Talks
entry.content: Russian forces moved by air and land to attack Kyiv and the capital’s defenders dug into positions and deployed for urban combat, while Moscow signaled openness to holding talks with Ukraine’s government.
